71
00:04:18,007 --> 00:04:21,602
I mean, look at Wolowitz. He's not English,
but he's dressed like Peter Pan.

72
00:04:23,279 --> 00:04:26,942
Sheldon is neither sound nor light,
but he's obviously the Doppler effect.

73
00:04:31,621 --> 00:04:35,113
- I'm not Peter Pan, I'm Robin Hood.
- Really?

74
00:04:35,558 --> 00:04:38,857
<i>Because I saw Peter Pan
and you're dressed exactly like Cathy Rigby.</i>

75
00:04:40,430 --> 00:04:44,264
